	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Tashan and Malise spell lines are the only true way to lower resists. Some mobs (very few, all high level) have effective resistance increased if the caster is out of melee range however.<br><br>Beyond that, nothing else works.<br>&nbsp;<br>Zyphyr Runnersbane<br>60th Vending Machine<br>Cult of the Ancient Wyrm<br>Solusek Ro<br></td></tr>
