	   <tr><td colspan=2>Whether you can tank or not depends on many things-- AC, level, equipment, the group you are with, how your skills have been kept up (offense and defensive skills), the type of mobs you are fighting, and how willing you are to take a beating.<br><br>It can be done, just not as effectively as a true tank/warrior.&nbsp;&nbsp;Hope this helps!<br><br>Good luck, young troll shammies!<br>&nbsp;<br>Emperor and Shamanic High Priest of the Trolls<br>"Worship Innoruuk, you worthless cattle!"<br></td></tr>
