	   <tr><td colspan=2>In West Freeport, there is a tavern called The Hogcaller's Inn.&nbsp;&nbsp;Located inside are Lady Shae, Pahdos Flintside, and Jyle Windshot.  Anyway, these guys all have quests that reverse the faction you get for killing them.  For Lady Shae, you walk downstairs and buy her some wine.  For Jyle Windshot, you go buy him a small lantern.  But best of all, for Pandos Flintside (stupid dorf), you go to "Brownloe Bakery" and buy him muffins that cost no more than 8cp apiece.  Pandos is my favorite, since he drops usually about 5pp a kill, and is great experience (he is level 28, and Jyle Windshot is 30).  Sorry, i found out about this too late to get all the info on Lady Shae, but in order to get Pandos to go away, say "brownloe bakery".<br><br>Profuse Li<br>30 Barbarian Shaman<br>The Nameless<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
